      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for taking a look at my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let her go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this beauty. I\u2019ve kept this car in what I can only describe as pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and treated like a member of the family. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. You might find a tiny, barely-there mark from the road if you really go looking, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as you can get. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate how special this one is!",
